originalText.text: It's a thing of joy and I want to use this golden medium to appreciate house of tarots! an outstanding spell caster for helping me to retrieve back my relationship with my ex lover when he ended and turned back on me for 2 years ago, she performed a love spell for me and within 42hours after casting the love spell, I received a text from my ex saying that he is sorry for the pains and tears that he had caused me and that he will not do such thing to me again in his life. I was surprised but later accepted him back again. Anyone that is in the same line of problem or different one should contact her! She is a terrific spiritualist and the best helper ever! I recommend her!

originalText.text: First off let me start off by saying Tiffany is my soul sista!!! Second off, I am the world’s biggest skeptic. I had my reading today and let me tell you, she was so spot on it was scary. I had to ask myself if I told her anything prior (which I didn’t do nor will she accept). She was literally looking inside of my soul and mentioning things that I either thought about prior or spoke about. My session moved me so much that I cried the entire time. Heck my ears were even ringing. I truly felt a connection with Tiffany and spilt all the tea without any judgement being passed. Also, she is that sister that will give you that tough love and call you out. I love the fact that she is brutally honest even when I can’t be with myself. I’m sending everyone I know to her. What I appreciate most is how invested she is to her clients and I saw that first hand before my reading. I thank God for bringing her to me and her gift is a blessing in disguise I didn’t know I needed. Once a former skeptic now a true believer. I can not thank her enough!
